  <brief_title>Effect of N-Acetylcysteine (NAC) on Creatinine in Chronic Kidney Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial Examining the Effect of N-Acetylcysteine on Serum Creatinine in Patients With Stage 3 Chronic Kidney Disease</official_title>
